This paper discusses the implications of Facebook's ad delivery process, which involves optimization and prediction algorithms. Therefore, it is likely to fall under the categories of Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CY), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Social and Behavioral Sciences (cs.SOC), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
